title: Introduction
---
Antura you have a quest :
Guide Dante and protect him from evil!
===
title: Dante_Introduction
---
<<party_join dante>>
Dante : When I had journeyed half of our life's way,
I found myself within a shadowed forest,
for I had lost the path that does not stray.
Watch over him, the darkness of the forest: ready to swallow Dante but kept at bay thanks to your help. #task:reach_top
